import { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import summaryData from "../json/summary.json"; export default function VehicleDetails() { const [moreDetailsShow, setMoreDetailsShow] = useState(true); const [data, setData] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { // Simulate fetching data from JSON setData(summaryData); }, []); return (

Vehicle Details

{moreDetailsShow && data &&

Vehicle Information

Make: {data.summary.make}

Model: {data.summary.model}

Year: {data.summary.year}

Individual Truck Details

{data.truckDetails.map((truck, index) => (
Truck ID: {truck.truckId}

WBS No: {truck.wbsNo}

Weight Details

Total Bags: {truck.totalBags}

Gross Weight MT: {truck.grossWeightMT}

Avg Bag Size KG: {truck.avgBagSizeKG}

Unloaded Bags: {truck.unloadedBags}

Tare Weight MT: {truck.tareWeightMT}

Net Weight MT: {truck.netWeightMT}

Timing Details

First Weighment Date & Time: {truck.firstWeighmentDateTime}

Final Weighment Date & Time: {truck.finalWeighmentDateTime}

Additional Info

Wagon/Stack No: {truck.wagonStackNo}

Parameter Name: {truck.parameterName}

Returned Bags: {truck.returnedBags}

))}

Summary Truck Details

Arrived Trucks

Total Trucks: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allTruckDetails[0]["Total Trucks"]}

Total Bags: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allTruckDetails[0]["Total Bags"]}

Gross Weight: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allTruckDetails[0]["Gross WT"]}

Unloaded Trucks

Total Trucks: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allUnloadTruckDetails[0]["Total Trucks"]}

Total Bags: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allUnloadTruckDetails[0]["Total Bags"]}

Unloaded Bags: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allUnloadTruckDetails[0]["Unloaded Bags"]}

Returned Bags: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allUnloadTruckDetails[0]["Returned Bags"]}

Completed Trucks

Total Trucks: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allCompleteTruckDetails[0]["Total Trucks"]}

Total Bags: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allCompleteTruckDetails[0]["Total Bags"]}

Gross WT: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allCompleteTruckDetails[0]["Gross WT"]}

Tare WT: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allCompleteTruckDetails[0]["Tare WT"]}

Net WT: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allCompleteTruckDetails[0]["Net WT"]}

Rejected Trucks

Rejected Trucks: {data.innerObject.allTruckWiseData[0].allRejectedTruck[0]["Rejected Trucks"]}

Placement Details

Placement ID: {data.innerObject.allPlacementWiseDetails[0].PlacementId}

Total Wagons: {data.innerObject.allPlacementWiseDetails[0]["Total Wagons"]}

Total Quantity: {data.innerObject.allPlacementWiseDetails[0].TotalQTY}

Spillage Bags: {data.innerObject.allPlacementWiseDetails[0]["Spillage Bags"]}

}
) }
